Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.11,0:00:05.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然图书委员赤井前辈好可爱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.61,0:00:07.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有没有男朋友呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.74,0:00:09.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.45,0:00:13.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你一如既往对这种话题反应很迟钝啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.33,0:00:14.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.58,0:00:19.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有个相同年级的美女姐姐就会那样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.87,0:00:21.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 并不是…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.09,0:00:24.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了 ？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.84,0:00:27.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有种不祥的预感
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.55,0:00:32.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.43,0:00:37.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我二宫诚的双胞胎姐姐 二宫爱
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.68,0:00:42.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明只要闭上嘴老实待着还相当不错
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.08,0:01:08.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无论何时弟弟被姐姐踹都不需要理由
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.01,0:01:15.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那脚上的恶习无法无天
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.76,0:01:21.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作为弟弟 不禁担心起姐姐的将来
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,//===============TEXT===============
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.44,0:03:19.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又遇上了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.83,0:03:35.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这难道是情书
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.93,0:03:42.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.18,0:03:43.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那封信是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.06,0:03:52.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一二三四
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.35,0:03:55.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,五六七八
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.06,0:03:58.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一二三四
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.57,0:04:00.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,五六七八
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.26,0:04:03.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}一 二 三 四
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.24,0:04:03.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.85,0:04:06.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}五 六 七 八
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.53,0:04:06.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才的信是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.16,0:04:08.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好  OK
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.83,0:04:09.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来是跑步哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.29,0:04:10.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.66,0:04:13.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各自按自己的步调跑就好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.33,0:04:15.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么出发
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.29,0:04:17.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等 姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.29,0:04:35.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在努力呢 佩服佩服
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.55,0:04:41.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐 关于刚才的信
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.01,0:04:46.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是哪个啊  那个
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.51,0:04:50.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙是寄信人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.64,0:04:54.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是今年开始同班的人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.52,0:04:58.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是哪粗犷的棒球青年…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.19,0:05:01.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是明明没说过几句话
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.32,0:05:05.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底是为什么才在鞋箱里放信
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.99,0:05:14.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说道鞋箱里的信的话当然是情书了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.58,0:05:17.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐难道也迎来了春…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.58,0:05:19.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 不是难道
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.77,0:05:41.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然是那样么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.03,0:05:45.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那种像害羞少女一样的反应是啥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.65,0:05:49.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会让人状态失常啊 姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.20,0:05:54.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要怎么办…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.16,0:05:58.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还没读过信吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.17,0:06:00.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还没
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.00,0:06:04.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总之读一读吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.05,0:06:13.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是适合进行社团活动 挥洒青春的好天气呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.89,0:07:17.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.27,0:07:27.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这封信 是给我下面鞋箱那孩子的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.82,0:07:33.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.82,0:07:35.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让她受到如此耻辱
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.53,0:07:37.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她一定很生气
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.12,0:07:39.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那名棒球青年有人身危险
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.53,0:07:42.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 比起那  首先…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.70,0:07:45.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这时候会先冲着我来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.04,0:07:48.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没看
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.42,0:07:50.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那封信…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.55,0:07:53.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只看了最开始的收信人名字
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.47,0:08:03.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.27,0:08:09.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来 回去继续社团活动吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.32,0:08:15.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.20,0:08:16.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.03,0:08:18.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不生气吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.41,0:08:22.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完全不
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.58,0:08:28.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想那家伙写那封信的时候也一定很紧张呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.75,0:08:35.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在现今还做出在鞋箱里放信这么古风的事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.22,0:08:39.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且紧张到搞错鞋箱
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.01,0:08:44.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定现在脑袋里也全是信的事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.02,0:08:49.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做到那份上来将自己的心情传达给某人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.08,0:08:53.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是非常需要力量的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.46,0:08:57.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一二一二一二
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.67,0:08:59.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一二一二
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.01,0:09:03.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我啊  看到正在努力的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.72,0:09:05.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就会不由得高兴起来呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.97,0:09:07.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,光是有那种家伙在身边
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.56,0:09:09.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就会心情愉快
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.02,0:09:12.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.70,0:09:20.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}一二一二
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.90,0:09:20.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,fight
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.95,0:09:25.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看着正在努力的家伙就会获得力量
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.04,0:09:28.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就会觉得我也得努力了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.17,0:09:33.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以不如说是很感谢他呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.34,0:09:43.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天感觉见到了很多姐姐的意外之面
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.14,0:09:48.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以诚也要加油  成为好男人哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.27,0:09:50.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.02,0:09:55.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小点 闪光 我也来一起跑
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.36,0:09:57.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.03,0:10:04.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一二一二
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.08,0:10:07.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然作为弟弟
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.79,0:10:12.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,此时此刻还是不禁担心着姐姐的将来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.34,0:10:24.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我 二宫爱 非常担心弟弟的将来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.14,0:10:30.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诚那家伙 又堆了些无聊的东西啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.06,0:10:34.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.52,0:10:38.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管过多久都是不会收拾的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.86,0:10:41.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.99,0:10:46.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然是我们入部那年的？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.74,0:10:48.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还留着这种东西啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.62,0:10:55.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚入部的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.50,0:10:57.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看着这个开心了好几个小时来着呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.07,0:11:03.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是塞满了回忆啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.53,0:11:13.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,过剩的回忆也当不成陪嫁哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.42,0:11:24.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然作为姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.59,0:11:29.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,此时此刻还是不禁担心着弟弟的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.69,0:11:46.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她的名字是大木双叶
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.74,0:11:48.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爱称是小点
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.03,0:11:52.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好 闪光
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.37,0:11:54.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好 天气真棒呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.25,0:11:59.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是在高中交到的最好的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.13,0:12:02.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,修长的四肢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.88,0:12:06.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像模特一样的高个子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.34,0:12:10.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,光泽柔顺的乌黑长发
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.22,0:12:15.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然她是个大美女
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.81,0:12:17.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但不仅仅如此
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.19,0:12:21.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凛然的姿势
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.86,0:12:22.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不经意的动作
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.44,0:12:24.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,四周环绕的氛围
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.20,0:12:30.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小点的存在感与普通人不同
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.62,0:12:32.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么什么什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.08,0:12:34.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没什么哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.21,0:12:40.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.63,0:12:43.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各自找空着的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.59,0:12:45.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,迅速完成测定哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.80,0:12:54.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真讨厌呢 我没什么体力 而且
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.06,0:12:58.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那边  台阶测试空出来了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.02,0:13:01.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 谢谢…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.73,0:13:07.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,闪光？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.34,0:13:10.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀 小点？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.26,0:13:14.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,闪光？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.64,0:13:18.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,闪光
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.73,0:13:19.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 那边那位同学
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.48,0:13:25.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,台阶测试做过了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.90,0:13:28.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 还没
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.90,0:13:31.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找到小点了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.57,0:13:33.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是2班的大木同学吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.99,0:13:34.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.95,0:13:36.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道做法吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.16,0:13:37.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.12,0:13:40.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好僵硬
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.12,0:13:42.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 开始
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.50,0:13:46.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小点
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.50,0:13:49.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,重整旗鼓 开始
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.59,0:13:50.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.01,0:13:55.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你没事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.51,0:13:56.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太僵硬了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.47,0:14:01.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然小点平常都很成熟稳重
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.89,0:14:03.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小点
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.03,0:14:13.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,闪光
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.08,0:14:26.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有时会变得像小狗一样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.63,0:14:28.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一起转吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.89,0:14:36.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,33k
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.27,0:14:42.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,15k 这也真是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.02,0:14:44.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好柔弱…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.52,0:14:48.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,立位体前屈 现在空着哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.94,0:14:50.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.90,0:14:52.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢 谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.15,0:14:54.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.16,0:15:02.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我这是不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.37,0:15:07.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明还没跟班里同学熟悉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.79,0:15:11.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,却一下子被放进这么大群人中
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.55,0:15:14.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就不知所措了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.26,0:15:20.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.18,0:15:22.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像这样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.73,0:15:28.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有闪光在一起的话
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.65,0:15:31.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对于我来说
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.79,0:15:39.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}之后是50米跑
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.09,0:15:42.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}做完的人请移动到操场去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.69,0:15:35.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是帮了大忙了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.26,0:15:42.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不擅长运动 好累
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.76,0:15:48.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我真是什么都做不好的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.89,0:15:54.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然小点这么说 但我却不这么认为
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.02,0:15:59.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各就各位  预备
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.58,0:16:11.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 下一组
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.50,0:16:16.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各就各位  预备
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.38,0:16:22.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看 只要去做就能做好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.97,0:16:23.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.36,0:16:41.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小点
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.82,0:16:46.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才  你在中途放弃了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.66,0:16:49.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行  得要好好做啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.62,0:16:52.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是的 这就是实力
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.50,0:16:56.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我不擅长运动
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.63,0:17:00.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的不擅长运动
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.47,0:17:08.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 明白了  交给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.76,0:17:13.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小点有个坏习惯  那就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.52,0:17:18.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.57,0:17:22.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作为体力测定的最终项目
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.44,0:17:24.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本日的主菜登场了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.86,0:17:27.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是1000米跑哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.12,0:17:32.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讨厌 非常讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.66,0:17:33.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要说讨厌什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.12,0:17:37.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个长跑实在是讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.33,0:17:41.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是遇到讨厌的事会马上逃走
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.88,0:17:45.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反正也是倒数第一 真想放弃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.76,0:17:49.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为那样的小点送上珍藏的魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.64,0:17:52.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小点 小点
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.47,0:17:54.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,耳朵凑过来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.52,0:17:55.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.88,0:18:04.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各就各位 预备
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.85,0:18:17.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 那边 在干啥  跑起来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.85,0:18:18.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.86,0:18:21.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听好了 小点
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.82,0:18:26.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出发时一定要在最末尾起跑哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.15,0:18:31.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尽量不要累到 不要累到
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.58,0:18:36.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,珍藏的魔法咒语是「慢慢来」
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.42,0:18:39.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「慢慢来」
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.13,0:18:40.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.05,0:18:45.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 最后一圈
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.47,0:18:51.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用尽全力 冲刺
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.55,0:18:54.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,重要的是做事方法和思维方式
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.81,0:19:02.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎样？小点
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.61,0:19:04.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心情爽快吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.53,0:19:09.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能因为讨厌的事就连心情也阴郁哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.46,0:19:29.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.88,0:19:32.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要死了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.72,0:19:39.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为  长跑 就是 要死的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.35,0:19:43.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.65,0:19:46.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好  闪光是4分32秒
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.15,0:19:48.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小点是34秒
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.19,0:19:50.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你俩都是7分
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.99,0:19:55.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姑且排名上闪光是第10  小点是第11
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.24,0:19:57.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.70,0:20:01.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是再早点冲刺的话
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.42,0:20:04.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或许能再超过一个人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.34,0:20:11.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想再跑一次
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.66,0:20:27.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗 小点你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.88,0:20:29.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.34,0:20:32.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小点你应该是不服输吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.63,0:20:35.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定是的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.51,0:20:39.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不服输 …我…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.39,0:20:45.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,至今为止没被那么说过
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.44,0:20:49.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也至今为止完全没发觉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.40,0:20:51.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用了  那种事情用不着发觉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.78,0:20:55.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为更加了解小点了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.15,0:20:57.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.28,0:21:03.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我第一个发觉小点的崭新一面也令我高兴呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.79,0:21:13.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管有多么喜欢 觉得有多了解
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.92,0:21:16.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也会有很多不了解的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.51,0:21:19.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发现了那些事情的话
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.14,0:21:24.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就会像是发现了宝物一样心情激动令人高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.39,0:21:27.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又会变得更加喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.52,0:21:32.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又是美女又很成熟 偶尔像个狗狗一样
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.27,0:21:31.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}喂 集合
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.19,0:21:34.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}走吧 小点
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.19,0:21:36.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}走吧 闪光
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.23,0:21:34.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实是个不服输的人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.90,0:21:37.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我那令我骄傲的朋友 在今天
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.57,0:21:41.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,变得更加更加令我骄傲了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.95,0:21:46.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不服输的小点也很棒哦
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,//===============NEXT===============
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.03,0:23:27.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看上去能很轻易过去
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.70,0:23:29.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,却无法马上过去的距离
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.24,0:23:34.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我本以为有这手机上的照片就没问题了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.25,0:23:36.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下集蓝海少女
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.92,0:23:38.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无法消去的回忆的事
